title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Jun 24 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Jun 24 2022
description:
Buck celebrates the Supreme Court overturning Roe v Wade. Ann Coulter discusses the Supreme Court decision today on Roe v Wade. Fox Business Network Host Larry Kudlow joins buck to discuss inflation, gas prices & the economy. Clay Travis calls in on his day off to talk with Buck about the landmark Supreme Court decision overturning Roe v Wade.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
